      "title": "v4.1 [CMD-2] Add project filter dropdown in Command header — scope all panels + kanban to one project",
      "description": "All tasks from all projects are mixed. Add a project selector in the header that filters tasks/backlog/done across both strategic and kanban views. Derive project list from task titles + sessions. 'All' as default option.",
