      "id": 100,
      "title": "v4.1 [CMD-4] Later panel: add sort controls (priority/date/title) + expand/collapse per project group",
      "description": "Currently 4-task cap per group, no sort, completely read-only. Add: sort toggle (priority desc, newest first, alpha). Expand/collapse per project group (default collapsed at 4, expand shows all). Add quick-action: click task → move to in_progress.",
