      "id": 101,
      "title": "v4.1 [CMD-5] Next panel: cache last plan in localStorage + make gap items actionable (create task from gap)",
      "description": "Plan is empty on every page load — user must click Plan each time. Cache the last AI plan in localStorage with timestamp so it persists across reloads. Show 'Generated Xm ago' label. Gaps: add a '+' button per gap to create a task from it directly.",
