      "id": 102,
      "title": "v4.1 [CMD-6] Done panel: show actual task duration (created→done) not just 'Xm ago' + fix critique to show today not all-time",
      "description": "Done panel shows 'Xm ago' (when finished) but not 'took Ym' (how long). Calculate created_at→updated_at duration. 'Took Longest' shows all-time slowest (#95 at 612m from weeks ago) — filter to this session or today. 24h window is arbitrary — use 'this session' as default.",
