      "id": 3,
      "name": "Nexus",
      "content": "# Nexus Client GUI Audit (v3.0-alpha5)\n\nAudited 4219 lines across 27 .jsx/.js/.css files.\n\n## Dead Code (delete or wire up — pick one)\n- **Scratchpad.jsx** (284 lines) — fully functional, NOT in App.jsx, SearchModal links to it but nav fails silently\n- **Ledger.jsx** (140 lines) — fully functional, NOT in App.jsx, merged into Graph but file remains\n- **UsageGauge.jsx** (102 lines) — explicitly removed from Sidebar, orphaned\n- **ActivityHeatmap.jsx** (162 lines) — never imported anywhere\n\nDecision: delete UsageGauge + ActivityHeatmap (replaced by Fuel module).\nFor Scratchpad/Ledger: either re-add as hidden tabs or delete the .jsx files.\n\n## CLI/UI Asymmetry — 9 server features have ZERO client UI\n1. /api/thoughts (Thought Stack)\n2. /api/critique (Self-Critique)\n3. /api/guard (Decision Guard)\n4. /api/advice (Advice Journal)\n5. /api/predict (Predictive Tasks)\n6. /api/plan (Autonomous Plan)\n7. /api/auto-summary (Overseer auto-writes)\n8. /api/impact/forecast (AI migration assessments)\n\nThe CLI has 54 commands. The dashboard exposes maybe 20% of them.\n\n## Critical Bugs\n- **App.jsx**: SearchModal navigates to scratchpad module that does not exist — silent failure\n- **Sidebar.jsx**: ICON_MAP missing terminal entry — Terminal nav item shows blank icon\n- **No ErrorBoundary**: any module crash takes down the whole app\n- **MissionBoard.jsx**: drag-and-drop visual feedback never wires through onDragStart prop\n- **Fuel.jsx**: doesn't destructure ws in signature, breaking real-time updates\n\n## Cross-Cutting Debt\n- **Inconsistent fetch patterns**: 6+ components use raw fetch() instead of api.* helpers\n- **useApi.js**: missing 15+ endpoints (no thoughts, critique, guard, advice, predict, plan, auto-summary, forecast, heatmap, clock, digest)\n- **WebSocket under-used**: Pulse polls every 10s, Fuel every 30s, ClockWidget every 30s — should subscribe to push events\n- **Terminal.jsx** creates its OWN WebSocket instead of using useWebSocket hook\n- **No error toasts**: failed API calls fail silently across all modules\n- **No loading skeletons**: full-screen compass spinner is jarring\n\n## Mobile / Responsive\n- **Sidebar.jsx**: w-56 fixed, no hamburger toggle on <768px (eats 30% of mobile width)\n- **Fuel.jsx**: hardcoded grid-cols-2, never collapses\n- **Pulse.jsx**: lg:grid-cols-4 breaks badly at 1280px with sidebar\n- **MissionBoard.jsx**: drag-and-drop doesn't work on touch devices, no fallback\n\n## Accessibility Gaps\n- Compass spinners have no aria-label (3+ places)\n- Color-only status indicators (gauges) — no patterns for colorblind\n- Modal focus traps don't restore to trigger button\n- No skip links in Sidebar\n- Sessions expand button has no aria-expanded\n\n## Top 5 Fixes (do these first)\n1. **Wire missing modules + delete dead code** — 30 min — unblocks Scratchpad/Ledger or removes them cleanly\n2. **Consolidate fetch into useApi.js** — 45 min — fixes silent failures + adds 15 missing endpoints\n3. **Replace polling with WebSocket subscriptions** — 60 min — Pulse/Fuel/ClockWidget all should push\n4. **Mobile responsiveness** — 40 min — hamburger sidebar + responsive grids\n5. **ErrorBoundary + toast on failures** — 50 min — eliminates silent crashes\n\n## Top 5 Enhancements (after fixes)\n1. **Build Thought Stack module** — 90 min — first new feature with no UI\n2. **Add filter/sort to ActivityStream + Sessions** — 45 min — currently flat lists are unusable past 100 entries\n3. **Wire Decision Guard into MissionBoard** — 60 min — warn on duplicate task creation in the form\n4. **Keyboard shortcut matrix** — 30 min — Ctrl+S, Ctrl+D, Ctrl+/ help modal\n5. **Add auto-summary + forecast UI to Sessions and Graph** — 40 min — closes the wishlist gaps\n",
      "language": "markdown",
      "updated_at": "2026-04-07T13:38:46.364Z"
    },
