      "summary": "v1.4 Hybrid Smart Search. Reciprocal Rank Fusion merges keyword + semantic results. Type-boosted: decisions 1.5x, sessions 1.3x, activity 0.7x. CLI: nexus search. Dot product for speed. Shared embedding cache.",
