    {
      "id": 22,
      "project": "Nexus",
      "summary": "v1.5 Knowledge Graph shipped. Decisions now form a traversable graph with bidirectional edges. 5 relationship types: led_to, replaced, depends_on, contradicts, related. Auto-linker found 129 connections from 59 decisions using temporal chains (sequential in same project), keyword overlap (shared terms), and tag matching (cross-project). Zero orphan nodes. CLI: nexus link (manual), nexus graph (stats + traverse), auto-link API. Store: addEdge, removeEdge, traverse (BFS with depth limit), getGraph. Overseer can now traverse decision chains for deeper analysis.",
      "decisions": [
        "5 edge types sufficient for v1",
        "auto-link uses text overlap not AI (fast+free)",
        "BFS traversal with configurable depth",
        "zero orphans achieved"
