      "summary": "Massive session: v3.6→v4.0 Phase 2 + frontend restructure + pre-release audit + critical fixes. Shipped: v3.6.1 (5 Overseer self-audit fixes), v3.7 (frontend 10→7 modules with Command+Log merges), first successful Overseer code-audit (46k tokens, 15.7min on local GPU), AI semaphore (prevents LM Studio slot contention), aiFetch via undici (no 5min headers timeout), GPU signal tuning (lowered thresholds for CPU-bound generation, removed absolute timeout), v4.0 Phase 1 (self-contained MCP with in-process NexusStore at ~/.nexus/), v4.0 Phase 2 (Claude Code Plugin package with skills/agents/hooks), configurable PROJECTS_DIR (17 hardcoded paths → shared config.ts), file watcher feedback loop fix (478 spam entries purged), Command Now panel redesign (work metrics not fuel gauges), full Command audit with 7 tasks queued for v4.1.",
      "decisions": [
        "Command module Now panel shows actual CC work metrics (elapsed time, progress, session stats) not fuel gauges — fuel belongs in Fuel module",
        "File watcher needs PROGRAMMATIC filter for nexus data files, not just chokidar globs — rename events bypass glob matching",
        "AI semaphore (one inference at a time) + aiFetch (undici, no headers timeout) + GPU signal (lowered thresholds) = three-layer protection for local AI calls",
        "Self-contained MCP uses adapter pattern: localApi.ts mimics HTTP interface, tool handlers unchanged, only transport switches",
        "PROJECTS_DIR in shared config.ts with auto-detection (check C:/Projects first, then ~/Projects etc) — single source of truth for all 12 server files"
      ],
